history.text: Hey there! So, the movie I got is inception.  I really think it would be a good watch for you.
It was rated really highly on IMDB and Rotten tomatoes so that's already a good sign. Leonardo DiCaprio is the lead, he portrays a thief that steals information from peoples dreams.
One critic response states "wildly ingenious chess game" so if you're into deep psychological thrillers that's definitely another plus.
